rows.label: bf04070100_0010
rows.name:
Going back to Avaritia, ship to Superbia, then on to 
the Holy See is the shortest route.

rows.label: bf04070100_0020
rows.name: A guild ship might be at the port.

rows.label: bf04070100_0030
rows.name:
Then we can probably ride for free. 
Let's go and see.

rows.label: bf04070100_0050
rows.name:
Salvagers can ride for free. 
I'll try negotiating for Homura and the others too.
